name: Harald Hardtand i Kampenom de rene taender
name_original: Harald Hardtand i Kampenom de rene taender
description:
Harald Hardtand i Kampenom de rene taender is an arcade game developed by Breadline and Silver Rock Productions. It came out on 01-01-1992. Colgate-Palmolive published the game.
Harald Hardtand i Kampenom de rene taender is available on PC.
